  "prompt": "Which is a good inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center near Washington County AR?",
  "response": "There are several inpatient drug and alcohol rehab centers near Washington County, AR. Here are a few options to consider:\n\n1. **Ozark Guidance Center** - Located in Springdale, AR, they offer comprehensive addiction treatment services including inpatient care.\n\n2. **Willow Creek Behavioral Health** - Situated in a nearby area, they provide a range of behavioral health services including substance abuse treatment, often with tailored inpatient programs.\n\n3. **Recovery Centers of Arkansas** - They offer different types of treatment programs, including residential treatment options.\n\n4. **HealthStar Physicians** - While primarily a physician group, they can also provide referrals to various rehabilitation services in the area.\n\n5. **The Bridgeway** - Located in North Little Rock (a bit further away), this facility offers various addiction treatment services including inpatient care.\n\nIt's crucial to contact these facilities directly to gather information about their programs, insurance acceptance, and available accommodations. Additionally, consider looking for reviews or asking for recommendations from healthcare professionals or local support groups.",
